{
  "stem": "17001.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was more volunteers who wanted to go to the cemetery, because what happened is the first time when they went, there is also a cemetery guard who was guarding the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they made deals with the cemetery guard that he should have eggs and he should have milk and they would put it back into the casket, you know, because the Jewish people, they have like a carrier, a wooden carrier.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's where they put the plaque with the-- and then they put the food in there, so there was like a-- a business extraction from the cemetery back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So a lot of people wanted to go to the cemetery to carry the dead, and this way they were able to bring back the food.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And is really amazed me, I mean, that how resourceful people could get.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had enough food, because we getting the food from the kitchen and also the food that we have taken from home.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And once you have fat and you have flour, then you could make anything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, we-- we weren't hungry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had-- as a matter of fact, my mother was giving food to other people who didn't bring in anything because they didn't have anything to bring in to begin with.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then, as time was progressing and spring was in the air-- because we were taken away from our home on the 17--",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "April, April 17, and this was already end of April and beginning of May.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the trees were starting to bud and spring is in the air.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as much as it was a lot of tsuris around, a lot of hardship, the lovers were lovers anywhere you looked.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
